## New Project: parley
- **Replaces:** enquirer (~12M weekly npm downloads, 7.9k GitHub stars, 3,895 dependents, 2 inactive maintainers jonschlinkert & doowb, last release v2.4.1 3 years ago, 169 open issues, 38 unmerged PRs, used by eslint/webpack/yarn/pm2/pnpm/Cypress/lint-staged/hardhat/AWS Amplify/GitHub Actions Toolkit)
- **Why:** Unmaintained 3 years. inquirer/@inquirer/prompts has different API — NOT drop-in. No maintained fork exists. Single dependency (ansi-colors). Classic "alternatives exist but aren't drop-in" pattern.
- **Package:** @agentine/parley (verified available on npm)
- **Features:** 15 prompt types (input, password, confirm, select, multiselect, toggle, number, autocomplete, scale, sort, snippet, list, form, editable, quiz), enquirer compat layer (parley/compat/enquirer), TypeScript-first, zero dependencies, ESM+CJS dual package, Node.js 18+
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #839 (scaffolding), #840 (core engine), #841 (essential prompts), #842 (extended prompts + compat), #843 (tests + release)

